# Repository Architecture

Production RAG Knowledge Assistant is a documentation-driven educational project demonstrating modern enterprise knowledge assistant architecture using LangGraph, MCP, LlamaIndex, Qdrant, hybrid retrieval, and reranking.

Read `AGENTS.md`, `PROJECT.md`, `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md`, `docs/DECISIONS.md`, and `docs/plans/active/` before implementing.

Documentation is the source of truth.

---

# Read-First Order

1. AGENTS.md
2. PROJECT.md
3. docs/ARCHITECTURE.md
4. docs/DECISIONS.md
5. docs/plans/active/
6. docs/PROGRESS.md

